        <content><![CDATA[<div>
 <h1 class="title topictitle1">Edit a guided tour</h1>
 <div class="body taskbody role-sn_tourbuilder.tour_admin"> 
  <ol class="ol steps"><li class="li step stepexpand"> <span class="ph cmd">In the Guided Tour form, take any of the following actions.</span> 
    <ul class="ul choices" id="sys_embedded_tour_guide-normal__d32558e69"><li class="li choice">Edit the name.</li><li class="li choice">Enter a different page name in the <span class="ph uicontrol">Context</span> field. For example, if the form page is listed and you want the user to start on the list view to enter a new record.</li><li class="li choice">Enter or edit the description.</li><li class="li choice">Clear the <span class="ph uicontrol">Active</span> check box to disable the guided tour. Consider inactivating the tour until you are finished editing it. Select the check box to enable the tour when it is ready.</li></ul> </li><li class="li step stepexpand"> <span class="ph cmd">To apply text formatting in the step instructions, click the step number in the <span class="ph uicontrol">Guided Tour Steps</span> related list and complete the following steps.</span> 
    <ol class="ol substeps" id="sys_embedded_tour_guide-normal__d32558e99"><li class="li substep substepexpand"> <span class="ph cmd">Scroll to the <span class="ph uicontrol">Content</span> HTML formatter.</span> </li><li class="li substep substepexpand"> <span class="ph cmd">Edit the content and apply formatting as appropriate.</span> 
      <div class="itemgroup info"> 
       <div class="note note"> 
        <span class="notetitle">Note:</span> Do not add images or video to the text. These media types do not render in the callout text box. 
       </div> 
      </div> </li><li class="li substep substepexpand"> <span class="ph cmd">Click <span class="ph uicontrol">Update</span>.</span> </li></ol> </li><li class="li step stepexpand"> <span class="ph cmd">To work with the tour steps, click <span class="ph uicontrol">Edit with Designer</span> in the form header.</span> 
    <div class="itemgroup stepresult">
      The target UI page opens in the GTD in a new tab or window. 
    </div> </li></ol> 
 </div>
